      "content": "that makes sense for a debate context. can u expand on the \"social cohesion\" part? like, what were the specific arguments about how mixing different racial groups would actually harm a neighborhood's economy or its sense of community? i want to be able to articulate the actual logic used back then so my rebuttal is more precise.",
